	<ul style="color: #000000; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: normal;">
<li><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Zong Yih Rubber Industrial Company is one of the leading manufacturers of connector systems boot, ball joint boot, industrial rubber products and custom molded rubber parts in Taiwan. Founded in 1978, engineers and molds custom rubber parts for OEM and aftermarket industries. Located in Taiwan, we began by serving the wide variety of industries and manufacturers that make up the industrial heartland of Taiwan.<br /><br /></span></li>
<li><span style="font-size: 12pt;">With growth, we have expanded to serve customers world wide. We are fully integrated, with capabilities from material and tool development through full production.<br /><br /></span></li>
<li><span style="font-size: 12pt;">At Zong Yih, our products range includes sealing devices such as o-ring, v-ring, u-cups, and hydraulic and pneumatic seals and custom molded products such as rubber grommets, bumpers, bushings, isolation mounts, packing, rubber gaskets, boots, rubber bellows, pneumatic tool grips and R/C car tires.<br /><br /></span></li>
<li><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Today Zong Yih Rubber and its affiliates employ over 100 people and has 40,000 square foot factory is located in Taiwan.<br /><br /></span></li>
<li><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Over the last three decades Zong Yih has built a reputation for honesty and reliability. The company's tremendous growth has been fueled largely by their belief that producing excellent quality products is the best method of advertising.</span></li>
</ul> 
			
				
